Though he no longer commands the Enterprise, Admiral James Tiberius Kirk has never stopped making a difference.

Kirk’s tenure as a member of the Starfleet brass has been nothing short of historic. From stopping the homicidal Augment leader, Khan Noonien Singh, to navigating a murky peace process with the Klingons, this legendary figure in Starfleet has continued to sow the seeds of history wherever he walks.

Despite all these achievements, however, Kirk still feels the call of the captain’s chair. He longs to break away from the summits, the delegations, and the hearings. He longs to step foot on a starship again, to explore strange new worlds, to seek out new life and new civilizations... Just like the old days.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
