“Peace is a profitable illusion.”

Born to a wealthy family on the Orion homeworld, Naga Delvos was a prodigy. After mastering calculus at age six and forming her first cabal at age twelve, it was clear to all who knew her that she was destined for greatness.
Then came the Emerald Chain.
Formed from the ashes of the old Orion Syndicate, the Emerald Chain rose to power in the wake of the Burn. Establishing a brutal order where there was chaos, they quickly established their dominance over Orion territory.
Naga, knowing what fate awaited criminals under the watchful gaze of the Chain, elected to focus her keen mind on climbing that blood-encrusted ladder instead.
The determined young woman rapidly rose through the ranks, becoming a favored Enforcer of the Chain’s enigmatic leader, Osyraa. Her quick wit, sharp mind, and willingness to shed blood made her an ideal lawbringer.
Still, something stirs in Naga’s heart. The blood of Orion pirates runs through her veins. A renegade’s heart beats in her chest. There may be more destiny left to fulfill for Naga Delvos after all.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
