<color=#40CFFF>FACTION:</color> INDEPENDENT

If you could save your people from destruction while damning yourself in the process, would you do it?
Annorax of the Krenim Imperium was a brilliant man. Intelligent, cunning, and fiercely devoted to his people. He pledged to stop at nothing to restore the Krenim to their rightful place as a dominant power in the galaxy.
Desperate to protect his people from their age-old enemies, the Rinar, Annorax discovered a method of pushing elements out of the space-time continuum, thereby creating an alternate timeline where that element never existed.
This science was weaponized immediately.
In the years that followed, the Krenim became an unstoppable force in the Delta Quadrant. That is, until they were ultimately defeated by Kathryn Janeway and the crew of the USS Voyager.
Driven by naught but an unquenchable desire for revenge against Janeway, Annorax has launched a full-scale temporal invasion of the Alpha Quadrant. This time, we may not have Janeway to save us...', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
